name: At least one has to reach...
name_original: At least one has to reach...
description:
To warning to the humanity about an apocalyptic asteroid, 14 astronauts has to reach to their spaceship across a dangerous planet, where the only tool they have its... themselves.

Controls

Move: Left & Right Arrow

Jump: Space or Up Arrow

Head to the Spaceship

Beat all the 5 levels and reach to the Spaceship, to warn the earth about the asteroid.

May I use your corsep?

OF COURSE YOU CAN! In this planet, every tool has to be used, even the weird ones.

FUNFACT: Today, 09/07 its my Birthday
